data.description: GUARD GATED Tampa Bay Golf and Country Club, a 55 or better community presents an exceptional lifestyle just beyond the confines of your home. As a resident, you'll enjoy access to a Standard AND Championship golf course & pro shop! Restaurant, Bar, Tennis courts, pickleball courts, year round heated pool, cornhole games, bocce ball, shuffleboard, card games, dance club, dance floor, stage, entertaianment, talent shows and tons of community events! This IMMACULATE, barely lived in home (BUILT IN 2017, the newest for sale in this neighborhood) will please even the most selective buyers! Located in the SANCUARY AND BUILT BY K HOVNANIAN! Comprised of 2 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths, office, formal dining room, and extended 2 car garage PLUS an extended fully screened in, covered and tiled lanai. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a seamless flow of open living spaces, making it ideal for both relaxation and entertaining. Many new upgrades have recently been added such as: New paint inside & out, New upgraded lighting in kitchen & dining room, New LG refrigerator, New LG dishwasher, New extended, screened & tiled lanai with privacy & sun shades, 6 new palm trees, Curbing around entire home & mulch was recently replaced with new granite rock, Epoxy driveway, Replaced carpet with new commercial grade waterproof Luxury vinyl in both bedrooms & office. New professional landscaping. THIS ALMOST NEW HOME IS ABSOLUTELY BEAUTIFUL AND MOVE IN READY!!! Get ready to make memories that will last a lifetime! Your Florida dream home awaits, you will be enjoying the Florida resort lifestyle in your new home as quickly as you are able to move in! Gorgeous curb appeal on this full block home with stucco elevation. Abundant 42" solid wood Cabinets, Granite throughout entire home. Walk-in Pantry, and Ceiling Fans. Plus.. Internet & cable, all yard maintenance, fertilizer & pest control are covered by HOA. The location of this residence is equally remarkable. Situated in close proximity to premier shopping destinations, and an array of dining options, you'll find yourself immersed in a vibrant golf community that strikes a perfect balance between exclusivity and convenience. Ride your Golf Cart to the club house & amenities right inside the neighborhood! Excellent location that is close to Advent Health Hospitals, BayCare Hospital, Florida Medical Clinic, Wire Grass Mall, Tampa Premium Outlet Mall, Krate at the Grove, Ice Rink, Sam's Club, Costco, Movie Theater, and plenty of Dining. Easy access to I75, 275, Tampa International Airport, Downtown Tampa and Florida's amazing beaches.
